# SentinelWatch

## Configuration

Bright Data API keys, AI/ML API keys, and other secrets.

### Required
- `BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY` — Bright Data API key
- `BRIGHTDATA_USERNAME` — Bright Data account username
- `AIML_API_KEY` — AI/ML API key
- `DATABASE_URL` — PostgreSQL connection string
- `SECRET_KEY` — App secret key (generate with `openssl rand -hex 32`)

### Optional
- `COGNEE_API_KEY` — Cognee agent memory
- `SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL` — Slack alert notifications
- `PAGERDUTY_API_KEY` — PagerDuty for critical alerts
- `SMTP_HOST`, `SMTP_PORT`, `SMTP_USER`, `SMTP_PASSWORD` — Email alerts

### Redeem Bright Data Credits
Promo code: `unlocked` (worth $250) at brightdata.com
